data.description: Premiere Wine Country location in the heart of Yamhill! Lovely home situated on 84.5 acres with great access. 34 acres have been identified and tested as ideal for planting a vineyard in the Yamhill/Carlton AVA. This charming home has tons of space through out featuring high vaulted ceilings in the spacious living room, the primary on the main floor, great sized kitchen, and a home office! Detached outbuilding has tons of space for projects. Bring your vision and don't miss this amazing investment opportunity. Soil Report attached!
